BUILD_STATS_ENABLED

public static final boolean BUILD_STATS_ENABLED
If statistics collection is enabled at build time, this is set to true. This can provide some optimizations for those of you who don't care to collect data about how fast the cache is processing requests.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

ITEM_EXPIRATION_ENABLED

public static final boolean ITEM_EXPIRATION_ENABLED
If Item expiration is enabled at build time, this is set to true. This allows expiration times to be set for individual items. Turning this off will speed up the tuner thread slightly.
